Package ghidra.util.prop

Class PropertySet

  • java.lang.Object
    • ghidra.util.prop.PropertySet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BytePropertySet, IntPropertySet, LongPropertySet, ObjectPropertySet, SaveableObjectPropertySet, ShortPropertySet, StringPropertySet, VoidPropertySet
    public abstract class PropertySet
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Base class for managing properties that are accessed by an index. Property values are determined by the derived class.
    See Also:
